{
  "stem": "23942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had nightmares, and I would scream at night, and the other children heard the screams.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They told me, you were screaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were saying something, and they didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Probably in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't understand, and that was the danger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the nuns protected me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told, maybe, the other children they shouldn't say anything to anybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I found after I was a while, there were a few other Jewish children hidden there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was one of a few.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember their names, but I remember that I found out there were other few.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Among the children, it-- you couldn't hide it completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the-- I had nightmares.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know if they had it, but I had nightmares.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I was afraid, but I had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, the nuns were as good as they could be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have much food, but the very, very, very, very minimum that you could survive on, they gave us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave, because there was very little food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a war going on, and the less they had, the less they could give the children, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But meanwhile, I think, you see, they were trying-- of course, as nuns, they had a duty to teach the children to be-- to show their religion to whoever was there, the Catholic religion.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a while-- I-- see, I knew that I was Jewish, and I was brought up Orthodox and I knew a little bit of the shamar.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the beginning, I used to say shamar, but after a year or two, I start forgetting it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were teaching me the Polish prayers, and I had to learn it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
